release_note: We ve rebuilt our routines feature based on YOUR feedback! You can now set individual actions to repeat on any schedule and set multiple routines to repeat on any given day. Thanks for all your feedback in making Shmoody the best app we can be!

Welcome to Shmoody 3.0! We ve heard your feedback and have been hard at work to a new and improved version of Shmoody with all of the most requested features and upgrades you ve been asking for!
